Love On The Right Course premieres this Saturday on Hallmark! I had golfed maybe FORE times prior to going into this film so yes you could say I was GREEN. A month and a half before Budapest I learned and practiced as much as I could. What an incredible challenge. It might’ve cost me my sanity but I did end up finding a love for the sport - an itch I’ll forever be trying to SCRATCH. ⛳️ ♥️

Love On The Right Course premieres tonight on @hallmarkchannel! 
Shooting in beautiful Budapest was nothing short of a dream. I was so excited to play a golfer - before every take I was so nervous I wouldn’t hit the ball or that I’d send it in a destructive direction. Thankfully that only happened a few times and I survived it because I had the incredible support of the most encouraging cast and crew every step of the way (including my buddy from Brenbury @marcus_rosner) what an adventure! Thank you @scainprod @leifbristow @britbristow, your faith in me was everything and I’m forever grateful. 🤍🌹🇭🇺
